        <updateDate>2024-06-21T18:40:59Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tax Relief for Victims of Crimes, Scams, and Disasters Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill reinstates the tax deduction for certain personal casualty losses (e.g., resulting from crimes, scams, natural disasters) by eliminating the suspension period (2018-2025) on such deduction.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also extends the period for filing an amended return for claiming personal casualty losses.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
